d astronomy at the\nlevel of adaptive optics or greater. However, until a clear reduction in the\ninterline background and the corresponding increasing in sensitivity is\ndemonstrated optimized OH suppression fibres paired with a fibre-fed\nspectrograph will at least provide a real benefits at low resolving powers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2012 23:04:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2013 05:40:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-12"}
