hts lead us to conjecture the complete quantum extension of the\nSchwarzschild spacetime: the black hole is evaporated via the Hawking radiation\nand meanwhile the quantum spacetime is largely extended from the classical one\nvia the quantum bounce, suggesting that the information paradox might be\nresolved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2012 09:21:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2013 12:17:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-28"}
